s) está %2$s, se recomienda encarecidamente activar esta integración!','Based on the script originaly posted to %1$sAnalytics Talk%2$s'=>'Basado en el script publicado originalmente en %1$sAnalytics Talk%2$s','This plugin is intended to be used by IT and marketing staff. Please be sure you read the
