					<code>&lt;?php if ( function_exists( \'gtm4wp_the_gtm_tag\' ) ) { gtm4wp_the_gtm_tag(); } &gt;</code>','Container code compatibility mode'=>'Modo de compatibilidad del código del contenedor','Turning OFF the Google Tag Manager container itself will remove both the head and the body part of the container code but leave data layer codes working.<br/>
